text: Small traditional stationary shop offering printing and lamination services and pickup of parcels services . Rare find these days I’d want to do simple photocopying or lamination

It may be hard to locate the shop but it’s basically behind the main road bus stop. The Indian owner is very kind to help receive shopee orders for you to pick up. It’s a old school mama shop with it’s own charm

It was difficult to locate the shop as I didn’t walk from the bus stop. It’s actually a convenient store own but Indian fam. From Geylang bus stop -> walk towards the Aljunied Dental Surgery shop -> it’s on the right side ☺️
Dishonest guy with very bad attitude! Didn't scan my Shopee packages and claimed he did!
The shop assistant / owner is very rude. Won't go back there again!
